e><br />\n係你太低分覺得你放蛇"},{"pid":"0e5a78e294d49219efe505b3b4c814fbd50e19b9","tid":329062,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:54:39.000Z","msg":"搭左左就快20次，4.72分"},{"pid":"aee546eb11b428f95f76b4bc9ba48cd9ecf09cdd","tid":329062,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>UBER 仲有得做咩<br />\n比人拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知 但冇理由個司機比分個客</blockquote><br />\n司機緊係可以比分個客<br />\n西客比1分，等其他司機唔好中伏</blockquote><br />\n其實客人個分有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢咪講左..."},{"pid":"a75898bf0a178c31d775b9e30a51c89c59ebb507","tid":329062,"uid":38648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:35:11.000Z","msg":"點樣睇個評分？<br />\n我搭過3次, 佢個faq話個分會顯示係Menu我個名下面但我打開Menu個名周圍都冇野"},{"pid":"e5314de346574f535cb42980f35704e4279c60c1","tid":329062,"uid":84046,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算把啦仲uber 我搭短程又要比你地評1分比我又乜乜柒柒話蝕埋油錢 咁我搭的士好過啦<br />\n搭長程更加唔使搭uber 的士差唔多價仲要熟路肯踩肯去 call van分分鐘仲平<br />\n有本事咪叫uber cut晒所有20km以下嘅單囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係鬧緊樓主 純粹見到uber po入嚟鬧吓交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 搭咗&gt;50次 評分4.02<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無可能同的士差唔多價，的士一公里$8.5,uberx一公里$5，愈長程uber愈平，基本上入大東北大西北機場最少比的士平幾十，仲無行李費電召費寵物費回程隧道費<br />\n<br />\nBtw,我自己有做司機有做客，uber唔同的士隨街接客，uber去pick up點接係要成本，基本上從接單到你可以上車最少用10幾分鐘，好彩既嚮附近5分鐘內接到，但好多時塞車，燈位都用好耐，最後到左仲要打比班上帝等佢斯斯然咁落樓上車，隨時用20分鐘以上先start trip。仲未計唔識用手機亂擺位置要司機兜同搵既人，以uberx而家呢個賤價價，10公里司機大概有$60-70，5公里以下得30幾。計埋塞車做你一單可能用半個鐘先收你幾十蚊，扣埋油錢司機基本白做，仲有d唔跳錶既基本蝕做。<br />\n<br />\n做得uber都係為左搵d錢，無邊個係義工心態，當然可以話食得咸魚抵得喝，所以司機咪比低分客比其他司機決定接唔接張單，唔介意既咪接黎做。另外客/司機比1星既話以後唔會配到對方，所以如果客成日比一星司機都會好難叫車。<br />\n<br />\nBtw,我自己做客做司機都係99%比5星，但同樣大部分時間會唔接d 4.5分以下既單<br />\n最過份係機場返東涌既客，因為第2次入carpark1係要比22$"},{"pid":"5ac42270c89155a51d3eccec8ae78be656a248bd","tid":329062,"uid":84046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:16:25.000Z","msg":"我自己第一眼睇個分決定接唔接<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/081618_d762840bc1c894ee4eb26e249e3fab9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F081618_d762840bc1c894ee4eb26e249e3fab9e.jpg&h=87327265&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/081619_6a047f4082048beecbd74815f1dd5efb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F081619_6a047f4082048beecbd74815f1dd5efb.jpg&h=2a783d23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79d1b6fd79085a54cebbad0b03555155e336b135","tid":329062,"uid":35514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/150623_3bc5f75aa42a8c61df6247d522dbc1ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F150623_3bc5f75aa42a8c61df6247d522dbc1ed.jpg&h=805249cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/150624_8b3afe14eb6dc64d001155c8cf4f724b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F150624_8b3afe14eb6dc64d001155c8cf4f724b.jpg&h=83fcf2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/150624_0db91a09a2859f050ecffe3894120454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F150624_0db91a09a2859f050ecffe3894120454.jpg&h=01414fad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/150625_a7032b114ff70107b3d007465390753b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht